[![](https://i0.wp.com/photos22.flickr.com/34627965_526e4f9ac3.jpg?w=960)](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/34627965/ "photo sharing") [Banksy No More](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/34627965/), originally uploaded by [Adam Tinworth](http://www.flickr.com/people/adders/).
It looks like the backlash against London’s [favourite (Bristolian) street artist](http://www.banksy.co.uk/) may have begun. **Update:** Our anti-Banksy graffiti artist isn’t nearly as clever as he thinks. It turns out that this particular piece of work is by [Arofish](http://www.arofish.org.uk/arofish/album19), and not Banksy after all.
